summary: Headcanon that the Doctors represent the hours of the day.
title: Headcanon that the Doctors represent the hours of the day.
body:
The first twelve were for 1am to 12pm and were men. Now the hour hand has finished a turn and it is time for the next twelve Doctors, and I hope they will be women.

Because I love the idea of a female Doctor and because we need it. I want an Asian Doctor, an African-American Doctor, a younger or older Doctor.

I just need more Doctor Who.
